Loki is for the MCP logging resource.
Grafana's Loki service gets and saves logs (via promtail) from some source and puts into grafana server (a go between from a log emitting source and grafana). It also allows LogQL fromatted queries in grafana service.

Grafana-Tempo is for the MCP Tracing resource.
Grafana's Tempo is for tracing requests through MCP flow.

Prometheus is for the MCP metrics resource.
Prometheus is the Grafana Metrics solution, scrapes metrics and put into grafana server (a go between from a metrics emitting source, and grafana).